# Prerequisites: You need to have a compiler set up (e.g., Visual Studio)\n\n# Clone the inclued extension source code\ngit clone https://github.com/php/pecl-tools-inclued.git\n\n# Navigate to the directory\ncd pecl-tools-inclued\n\n# Prepare the build environment\nphpize\n\n# Configure the build\n./configure --with-php-config=path/to/php-config\n\n# Build the extension\nmake\n\n# Install the extension\nmake install